metadata.name: Pixel Party Ape #1
metadata.description: **PUBLIC MINT IS CURRENTLY LIVE at https://bapp.club.**  Mint for only .09 ETH each while minting is still open.  *Welcome to the Bored Ape Pixel Party!*  The BAPP is a set of 10,000 Bored Ape NFTs inspired by the original BAYC collection.  Each colorful, AI-pixelated NFT is a one-of-a-kind collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.  Your Pixel Bored Ape also serves as your Club membership card, granting you access to exclusive benefits for Club members.
